    <text id="F8039T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Seibert asks Cameron for a patronage appointment to the Post Office.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Seibert<lb/><del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <hi rend="underline">Chamberburg</hi><lb/><abbr expan="November">Nov</abbr>
                    1860.
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1860-11-12"><abbr expan="November">Nov</abbr> 12/<abbr
                                expan="1860">60</abbr></date>
                        <name type="place">Chambersburg</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute><abbr expan="Honorable">Honr</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="Simon">S.</abbr> Cameron<lb/>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have helped many of my fellow men. Now I need help myself. Can I have yours. as
                    an applicant for the Post Office of this place-If so please cheer me up by the
                    welcome yes.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours, you well<lb/>know,</salute>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="underline"><abbr expan="William">Wm</abbr> Seibert</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
